{"descriptions":[{"id":1352,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eInterrogative sentences end with final interrogative particles, the precise form of which is determined by the last letter of the preceding auxiliary.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eངས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགས་\u003c/span\u003e is used after \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔས་\u003c/span\u003e is used in all other cases\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eFor example: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་པས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡོད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསོང་ངས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམྱོང་ངས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱུང་ངས་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདུག་གས་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eFinal interrogative particles are not used with these copulas and auxiliaries when a sentence already contains an interrogative pronoun (such as \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;what,\u0026rdquo; \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསུ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;who,\u0026rdquo; etc.).\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eHowever, with the verb \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e, a final interrogative particle \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔ་\u003c/span\u003e is sometimes used. If there is no interrogative pronoun in the question, the sentence ends with \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་པས་\u003c/span\u003e, the interrogative form of the verb \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e; if the question does contain an interrogative pronoun, the sentence ends in \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་པ་\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁྱེད་རང་དགེ་རྒན་ཡིན་པས།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Are you a teacher?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསུ་ཡིན་པ།\u003c/span\u003e = \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསུ་ཡིན།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Who are you?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:42 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:42 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}